item.title: CVE-2024-32535|2024-04-17T08:43:04.708Z -- Jojaba -- Access Category Password
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in Jojaba Access Category Password allows Reflected XSS.This issue affects Access Category Password: from n/a through 1.5.1.
